    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Polyurethane-94 is a complex urethane polymer formed by the reaction of Benzoic Acid, Dimethylolpropionic Acid, Isophorone Diisocyanate, Pentaerythritol, Phthalic Anhydride, Trimethylolpropane, Coconut Acid, and a mixture of fatty acids derived from Gossypium Herbaceum Seed Oil. The urethane polymer is reacted with Triethylamine to allow it to be dispersed into water."
